Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.78,0:02:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你想要做的事嗎
