Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榮子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是被那呆紅毛所傷？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.28,0:02:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和望一郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人悖逆了須原神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須告發他的陰謀
