Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋  你在愚弄我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「2V」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的代號
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照  小美人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開個玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼父親  這場戰爭的目的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將他打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥將由照屋榮子指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不是照屋家的當主？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬三被紗伊阿九斗殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動私情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們作為須原神信徒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使看不慣照屋家  目標也只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是家傳寶刀
